      <h2 class="block-title">Conversations at Edge</h2>
  
  <div class="block-content content"><ul class="related-conversations"><li class="related-conversation"><div class="title"><a href="/conversation/a-balloon-producing-balloons-producing-balloons-a-big-fractal-" class="title">A BALLOON PRODUCING BALLOONS, PRODUCING BALLOONS:A BIG FRACTAL</a></div><div class="author"><span class="byline">A Conversation with&nbsp;</span><a href="/memberbio/andrei_linde" class="title"><span class="author">Andrei&nbsp;Linde</span></a><span class="date"> [ 8.24.12 ] </span></li><li class="related-conversation"><div class="title"><a href="/conversation/the-inflationary-universe" class="title">THE INFLATIONARY UNIVERSE</a></div><div class="author"><span class="byline">by&nbsp;</span><a href="/memberbio/alan_guth" class="title"><span class="author">Alan&nbsp;Guth</span></a><span class="date"> [ 11.19.02 ] </span></li><li class="related-conversation"><div class="title"><a href="/conversation/a-golden-age-of-cosmology" class="title">A GOLDEN AGE OF COSMOLOGY</a></div><div class="author"><span class="byline">by&nbsp;</span><a href="/memberbio/alan_guth" class="title"><span class="author">Alan&nbsp;Guth</span></a><span class="date"> [ 12.2.01 ] </span></li><li class="related-conversation"><div class="title"><a href="/conversation/a-universe-in-your-backyard" class="title">Chapter 16
	"A UNIVERSE IN YOUR BACKYARD"</a></div><div class="author"><a href="/memberbio/alan_guth" class="title"><span class="author">Alan&nbsp;Guth</span></a><span class="date"> [ 5.7.96 ] </span></li></ul></div>
  </div></section><section id="block-views-e78546b5b0386070ffd1c0859ecbd2cb" class="block block-views" ><div class="block-inner clearfix">  
